race.description: Ladbrokes Future Stars Series Heat 8 Maiden Plate
race.comment: TEN WARRIORS (4) can't quite crack that maiden win but is going well and finds the right race here. He tackled a strong Class 3 at Ballarat two back over this trip and ran very well, just missing back to 1200m here last time as favourite. Like him back out to 1400m now and he sets the benchmark again. RICH KING (3) ran a strong race on debut at Cranbourne over this trip when beaten a length into third. He'll be better for that and can give a bold sight. I SAID SO (2) has placed in his past two and won't need to improve much to be figuring prominently again. CELESTRA (11) is coming along well and should improve out to 1400m now.
